
Crossfire
---------

Crossfire is a fork of Openfire aimed at being secure, reliable, and easily configurable.

Release 0.5

- Replace mina with netty to improve performance
- Finish rebranding as Crossfire
- Strip out all non-core functionality (will be reintroduced as plugins after its been reviewed)
- Refactor the core to be easier to understand and maintain
- Add additional unit tests 

